{"tid":2370693,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【送頭】納瓦爾尼疑遭俄羅斯投毒後逃至德國，今日返回俄羅斯立即遭扣留","createTime":"2021-01-18T08:18:13.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-18T10:14:06.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"cdedc4811074afc86b82237e48d650fa827822d3","tid":2370693,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T08:18:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1570936-20210118.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1570936-20210118.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=nfq7Ayl5XWctTRRkLGDCS4RM%2FwdnRWUJBfohchWxIRY%3D&h=3c74e9b0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1570936-20210118.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=f9b0a5a8\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1570936-20210118.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯反對派領袖納瓦爾尼從德國回國，抵埗後立即被扣留。美國及法國敦促俄羅斯立即釋放納瓦爾尼。<br />\n<br />\n美國國務卿蓬佩奧強烈譴責克里姆林宮當局拘捕納瓦爾尼，批評有關行為是要令納瓦爾尼及俄羅斯反對派噤聲的最新一次行動。獲美國候任總統拜登提名出任國家安全顧問的沙利文表示，俄羅斯應立即釋放納瓦爾尼，追究向他施襲的人士的責任，又批評俄羅斯當局侵犯人權。法國外交部發言人對納瓦爾尼被捕表示關切，呼籲立即將他釋放。<br />\n<br />\n今次是納瓦爾尼去年中毒轉送柏林就醫後，首次踏足俄羅斯。俄羅斯懲教部門表示，納瓦爾尼違反緩刑條件，自上月底被通緝，表示會羈留他直至法庭作出決定。"},{"pid":"5118263337b0cc1e1886c8f62c267076454a075b","tid":2370693,"uid":36995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T08:24:07.000Z","msg":"唔洗再向個世界<br />\n證明呢個政權惡毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d58d9e4377a3094ced2bf785d11fb032d37700ff","tid":2370693,"uid":182180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T10:06:46.000Z","msg":"點解佢要自首？"},{"pid":"352f950a84fd73ad881d85337c7b804c17d262db","tid":2370693,"uid":235152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d58d9e4377a3094ced2bf785d11fb032d37700ff","tid":2370693,"uid":182180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T10:06:46.000Z","msg":"點解佢要自首？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T10:14:06.000Z","msg":"俄特工好勁再唔返去就開槍做低佢,反而留俄未必死"}]}